{
  "screen_id": "obs-register-confirm",
  "route": "/observe/register/confirm",
  "title": "確認",
  "layout": "standard",
  "notes": "V3-AIP-101 観測登録スライス1(F5 1件版)。入力recap+「次の目安を登録」opt-outチェック(既定ON)+保存。保存 = POST /solid-observation/commit のみ(OBS-25 と同じ単一 commit ゲート)。value_origin は手入力系を明示付与(direct_observed)・サーバは補完しない。磨き直し(2026-07-12親レビュー): recapは前回値とのΔ表示付きカード(F6と同じ compare_* 部品・fix#9)。ステージ変化/死亡はこのスライスではF2で直接append-onlyコミット済み(F5合流のドラフト待ちキューは無い)ため、このスライスでは種別行は構造上発生しない — 新規のドラフト積み上げ機構は作らない。",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "shell",
      "type": "app-shell",
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "page",
          "type": "page",
          "children": [
            { "id": "title", "type": "heading", "props": { "text": "確認", "level": 1 } },
            {
              "id": "individual",
              "type": "card",
              "props": { "source_path": "/api/v1/individuals/{{params.individual_id}}" },
              "children": [
                {
                  "id": "recap-weight",
                  "type": "text",
                  "props": {
                    "text": "体重 {{params.weight_g}}g",
                    "compare_source": "individual",
                    "compare_item": "weight",
                    "compare_unit": "g",
                    "compare_current": "{{params.weight_g}}"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "recap-length",
                  "type": "text",
                  "props": {
                    "text": "体長 {{params.length_mm}}mm",
                    "compare_source": "individual",
                    "compare_item": "length",
                    "compare_unit": "mm",
                    "compare_current": "{{params.length_mm}}"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "confirm-form",
              "type": "form",
              "action": { "kind": "api", "method": "POST", "path": "/api/v1/solid-observation/commit", "body_from": "draft" },
              "props": {
                "static": {
                  "domain": "biology",
                  "subject_ref": "individual/{{params.individual_id}}",
                  "measurements.0.item": "weight",
                  "measurements.0.kind": "number",
                  "measurements.0.unit": "g",
                  "measurements.0.value": "{{params.weight_g}}",
                  "measurements.0.value_origin": "direct_observed",
                  "measurements.1.item": "length",
                  "measurements.1.kind": "number",
                  "measurements.1.unit": "mm",
                  "measurements.1.value": "{{params.length_mm}}",
                  "measurements.1.value_origin": "direct_observed"
                }
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "id": "register-schedule",
                  "type": "field",
                  "props": {
                    "variant": "checkbox",
                    "name": "register_schedule",
                    "label": "次の目安を登録 — {{date}} 頃(間隔30日・既定)",
                    "label_date_offset_days": 30,
                    "default": true
                  }
                },
                { "id": "commit-submit", "type": "button", "props": { "label": "保存", "variant": "primary", "type": "submit" } }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "transitions": [{ "from": "confirm-form", "to_screen_id": "obs-register-done", "label": "保存後に完了へ" }]
}
